data.description: Welcome to this stunning home situated on a spacious corner lot in a family-oriented neighborhood. Its prime location is in close proximity to all the schools, making it ideal for families. With large rooms and cedar-lined closets (except for the master), this home offers both comfort and luxury. The remodeled kitchen and pantry are a standout feature of this home, boasting modern design and functiona New paint in most areas adds to its appeal. Don't miss the opportunity to see this exceptional home. Its desirable location, recent updates, and spacious layout make it a perfect choice for families seeking a well-maintained and welcoming place to call home.
